<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .footer { background: #1e293b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
        .warning-box { background: #fef3c7; border: 2px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .contact-box { background: #f0f9ff; border: 2px solid #3b82f6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .security-notice { background: #fee2e2; border: 2px solid #f87171; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔐 Password Reset Request</h1>
            <h2>IGL AMC Dashboard</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h3>Hello {{name}},</h3>
            <p>We received a password reset request for your <strong>{{role}}</strong> account on the IGL AMC Dashboard.</p>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <h4>🚨 Security Alert</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                    <li><strong>Request Time:</strong> Just now</li>
                    <li><strong>Account Type:</strong> {{role}}</li>
                    <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> Protected for security</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h4>⚠️ Important Security Notice</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                    <li>If you <strong>DID NOT</strong> request this reset, please ignore this email</li>
                    <li>Your current password remains <strong>unchanged</strong> until you complete the reset</li>
                    <li>This security alert expires in <strong>30 minutes</strong></li>
                    <li>Never share your login credentials with anyone</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-box">
                <h4>📞 To Reset Your Password</h4>
                <p><strong>For security reasons, password resets must be handled by your system administrator:</strong></p>
                
                <table style="width: 100%; margin: 15px 0;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">📧 Email:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">admin@igl-amc.com</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">📞 Phone:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">+91-1234-567-890</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">🕒 Hours:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">Monday-Friday, 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM IST</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <h4 style="color: #3b82f6; margin-top: 20px;">📋 Information to Provide:</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px; color: #1e40af;">
                    <li>Your full name and employee ID</li>
                    <li>Email address associated with the account</li>
                    <li>Department and role designation</li>
                    <li>Reason for password reset request</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #10b981; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="color: #047857;">✅ What Happens Next?</h4>
                <ol style="color: #065f46; margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                    <li>Contact the administrator using the details above</li>
                    <li>Verify your identity with the required information</li>
                    <li>Admin will securely reset your password</li>
                    <li>You'll receive your new temporary password</li>
                    <li>Change to a permanent password on first login</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <p><strong>This process ensures the highest level of security for your IGL AMC Dashboard account.</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>© 2025 IGL AMC Dashboard</strong> - Professional Contract Management System</p>
            <p>🔒 This is a secure notification. Please contact admin for password assistance.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 10px;">
                Reset Token: {{resetToken}} (For admin verification only)
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
